Registro Uniforme de Evaluación del Sistema de Seguridad, Salud en el Trabajo y Protección Ambiental para Contratistas -  RUC®

Recognition by the Colombian Safety Council, of the effort and commitment to continuous improvement of Environmental Management Systems, Occupational Safety and Health, visible in the increased initial score qualification in 2013 from 76% to the current 83% in 2014, allowing Tubos Vouga to achieve the status of authorized user RUC® registered MARK.
 
It should be noted that providing the companies registered in the Register of Contractors Uniform (Suppliers) RUC® with a score above 80%, reflected in a substantial competitive increase with large clients of Petrochemical Industry and Cement.
 
The authorization of the RUC Mark is awarded by certificate issued by CCS for use of RUC® mark, taking into account compliance with the following requirements:
• Applies only to contractors of the oil sector and other contracting sectors;
• Rated firms under the assessment criteria RUC® and obtaining threshold of 80%;
• Do not introduce penalties labor, environmental, safety and occupational health for the use of RUC® brand;
• This certificate is valid until the classification would remain in force (one year);
• The RUC® brand; can be used in the company's advertising and is voluntary.

EHS Induction Training HYDRO Standardization developed & managed by Paula Hermogenes (EHS/5S Director for Hydro Business) with the inputs of all Alstom EHS Country Managers.

